## Third-Party Licenses

This project uses the following open-source libraries and resources:

### Fonts
- **Inconsolata**: Open Font License (OFL)
  - Source: Google Fonts
  - License: https://scripts.sil.org/OFL

- **VT323**: Open Font License (OFL)
  - Source: Google Fonts
  - License: https://scripts.sil.org/OFL

### Inspiration and References
This project draws inspiration from the following works, used under fair use:

- **The Matrix (1999)**: Visual effects inspiration
  - Matrix rain effect concept
  - Green-on-black terminal aesthetic

- **Blade Runner**: Color scheme inspiration
  - Cyberpunk atmosphere and mood
  - Neon color palettes

- **Neuromancer by William Gibson**: Conceptual inspiration
  - Cyberpunk terminology and themes
  - Digital world concepts

### No External Dependencies
This project is built entirely with vanilla web technologies:
- HTML5, CSS3, JavaScript (ES6+)
- No external JavaScript libraries or frameworks
- All code is original implementation

### Assets Attribution
All visual assets and code in this repository are original works created specifically for this project, except where noted above.

